divs: Sighting DetailsAt approx. 10:20 this evening (Friday Jan, 16th 2009) I saw two bright blue lights in the sky. What makes it unique is that it was very bright and considerably large. It was the color of a street light and I saw it through my window curtains that are almost opaque. I live close to the Polk Parkway in Auburndale and at the time I was facing North so if it was something like a meteorite it would be in the vicinity of Polk City.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Auburndale
There were no other sightings in Auburndale on or around January 16th 2009
